node.text: In this episodes of Hayes for Days, I show you my go-to breakfast, The BREAKFAST BURRITO! It's easy and tastes better the more love you put in. It's Hayes Cooks time.

node.text: About a year ago I got into mountain biking, I got a beater off craigslist and was riding it literally everywhere. Pretty much fell in love with it, going on rides a few times a week, 7/11, the whole 9. A couple months in I tested my luck a bit too hard and it got stolen. I was not happy about it as you can imagine. Today, my brothers surprised me with a brand new 2021 dime piece as an early birthday present. I can’t even tell you how much this means but you’ll see very soon. Thank you doesn’t even do it justice. You guys are the best. Now let’s go shred!!
